    "f, Losses of valid SMILES versus invalid SMILES sampled from a representative chemical language model trained on 30,000 or 300,000 molecules, classified into six different categories based on RDKit error messages (n = 10 7 SMILES; all p ≤ 1.1 × 10 -9, two-sided one-sample t-test).",
    "g, As in e, but for models trained on molecules from the GDB-13 database (p = 2.0 × 10 -11)."
